{"tid":124901,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩achiral molecule係有chiral centre?","createTime":"2017-02-18T04:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T15:48:30.000Z","uid":23619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f90b18a58fa3bb2dbb01d2614aad0cf3b791989","tid":124901,"uid":23619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T04:21:42.000Z","msg":"有冇啲簡單啲既molecule例子？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885f06662587bfcc9133ad0119b9ea2ee30b8e63","tid":124901,"uid":43652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T04:59:28.000Z","msg":"如果你係DSE考生 我會答你無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為根本無教我費事混淆你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事實上係有嘅<br />\n只要呢個compound有以下條件<br />\n-兩個或以上嘅chiral centre<br />\n-自身有reflectional symmetry<br />\n<br />\n咁樣呢個compound就可以superimposed in its mirror image 即係Achiral<br />\n但係佢又有chiral centres<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比個例子你<br />\n(2R,3S) 2,3-dichlorobutane<br />\n(2R,3S) 2,3-dihydroxybutanedioic acid <br />\n<br />\n呢種叫做Meso Compounds<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b39787949b348b98a000793189c46b334ca3f302","tid":124901,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T05:45:03.000Z","msg":"dse chem有教喎"},{"pid":"e6435bc0e60c412f156aa815c456a6054c9ad387","tid":124901,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T05:50:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>dse chem有教喎</blockquote><br />\nOutc 咁解jeh"},{"pid":"3043b3ffce31b9e1ae7828bb29156bd0c53b80f6","tid":124901,"uid":23619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:25:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你係DSE考生 我會答你無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為根本無教我費事混淆你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br /